\id PHM SAN MARTIN QUECHUA 
\h FILEMON 
\toc1 FILEMON PABLU FILEMONTA KILLKARKAN 
\toc2 FILEMON 
\toc3 File 
\mt1 FILEMON 
\mt2 PABLU FILEMONTA KILLKARKAN 
\c 1  
\s1 Pablu yachachikukmasin Filemonta rimachin. 
\p  
\v 1 Munanayni yachachikukmasini Filemon, ñuka Pablu kay karselpi kani Jesukristupa rimananta yachachikushkaynirayku. Wawkinchi Timoteowan tantalla kay kartata killkaykayki.  
\v 2 Wasikipi tantanakuk wawkinchikunata paninchikunata killkaykani. Paninchi Apiata trabajakmasini Arkipotapish killkaykani.  
\v 3 Munani Tata Diosninchi Señorninchi Jesukristuwan yanapashunaykichipa kushichishunaykichipa. 
\s1 Pablu Tata Diosta agradesin Filemon payta kuyaptin. 
\p  
\v 4 Tata Dioswan parlanayni oras kanta yuyashpayni payta agradesini.  
\v 5 Yachashkani sukaman Señorninchi Jesukristuta kreyishpa kuyashpa kawsanaykita. Yachashkani Jesukristuta kreyikmasinchikunatapish kuyanaykita. Chayrayku Tata Diosta agradesini.  
\v 6 Kan tukuy pita parlachinki Jesukristuta kreyikunaykita. Chayrayku Tata Diosta roygani allita entiendinaykipa Jesukristu sukaman kuyawashpanchikuna tukuy layapi yanapawananchikunata.  
\v 7 Kan, wawkini, Jesukristuta kreyikmasinchikunata kuyashpa kushichinki. Chayrayku ñuka sukaman kushikushpa animukuni. 
\s1 Pablu Filemonta roygan Onesimota perdonananpa. 
\p  
\v 8 Wawkini Filemon, Jesukristu ñukata kachamuwashkanrayku atipayman kamachiynikita imatapish kaptin ruranaykipa.  
\v 9 Chashna kamachiynikita atipashpaynipish mana nimapi kamachinayaykichu. Ñuka Pablu viejuna kashpa munani roygaynikita kuyawashpa kasuwanaykipa. Jesukristupa rimananta yachachikushkaynirayku kay karselpi kani.  
\v 10 Kay karselpi kaptini Onesimo yachachikushkaynita kreyishkanrayku kunanka ñami wambraynina. Chayrayku kay wambraynipa suk favorta mañayki. 
\p  
\v 11 Ñawpa tiempu Onesimo mana alli yanapashuk karkan. Kunanka ñukatana allita yanapawaykan. Kanman kutishpa kantapish allita yanapashunka.  
\v 12 Chayrayku kay munanayni wambrayni Onesimota kachaykani kanman kutinanpa. Kushikushpa ñukata chaskiwakshina paytapish chaskiy.  
\v 13 Jesukristu salvakuk kananta yachachikushkaynirayku ñuka kay karselpi kani. Chayrayku munayman Onesimo ñukawan kiparinanpa kan yanapawanaykishina pay yanapawananpa.  
\v 14 Kay wambrayni kiparinanpa munashpaynipish kan mana munaptiki mana kiparinkachu. Munayman tukuy shunku willanaykipa yanapawananpa. 
\p  
\v 15 Ichará alli kashka suk tiempullapa Onesimo sakishunanpa kashkan kutimushpa kanwan tukuy tiempu kawsananpa.  
\v 16 Kunanka Onesimota kuyadu wawkikitashina chaskiy. Manana rantidutashinanachu kaway. Ñuka wambraynitashina kuyani. Kanpish ñukamanta ashwanta kuyanayki tiyan. Payta kuyanayki tiyan runamasiki kaptin. Chaymanta ashwanta kuyanayki tiyan Jesukristuta kreyikmasiki kaptin. 
\p  
\v 17 Jesukristuta kreyikmasiki kanaynita yuyashpaykika Onesimota ñukatashina chaskiy.  
\v 18 Ichará wambrayni Onesimo dañuta rurashushpa nitikurkan. Debishuptikika ñukata kobraway.  
\v 19 Ñuka Pablu kay kartata makiniwan kikini killkashpa willayki pagaranaynipa. Chaymanta ama kunkaychu kanta yachachiptini Jesukristuta kreyinaykita. Chayrayku sukaman debiwanki.  
\v 20 Ariya wawkini, Jesukristuta kreyikmasini kashpayki yanapawashpa wambraynita chaskipay. Wawkini kashpayki kushichiway. 
\p  
\v 21 Chashna killkashpayni yachani kasuwashpa kay roygashkaynimanta ashwanta ruranaykita.  
\v 22 Chaymanta kankuna Tata Diosta roygaptikichi pay munaptin risha kawaknikichi. Chayrayku suk kuartuta allichapay chaypi chayanaynipa. 
\p  
\v 23 Wawkinchi Epafras Jesukristupa rimananta yachachikushkanrayku kay karselpi ñukawan tantalla. Paypish rimachishunki.  
\v 24 Tata Diospa rimananta yachachikukmasinikuna Markos Aristarkowan Demaswan Lukaswan rimachishunkisapa. 
\p  
\v 25 Jesukristuta roygani tukuy layapi yanapashunaykichipa. 
\p Ñuka Pablu chayllata killkashkayki.